Name: Fear Protocol: Codename Omega Starring Agent Jack Banger
About the game: It's a nice dark day in Escondido, California and special agent Jack Banger and his superior Gilbert Simpson are planning their next operation. Their life of luxury is soon interrupted however when strange biomonster creatures start appearing all over the city and the ominous Devil Corp is suspected of being the source of the chaos. The Night Striker Squad are sent in to investigate and stop the abominations from taking over the city. Only one question remains... Who is the traitor? GENRE Gripping Avant Garde Survival Shoot-Em-Up GAME INFO Control Agent Jack Banger with 3 deadly weapons to defeat the biomonster menace. Use your skills and cunning to solve puzzles and traverse down the HQ. PROS  Is Short  High Octance Action  Goes Out With a Bang CONS  Good Music  Defies Genre Stereotypes  Risotto
